title: Apple Earnings: iPhone Powers Growth, but Signs Point to a Slowdown
description: Consumers showed enthusiasm for the latest version of the phone, which helped the company increase total revenue by 8 percent in the latest quarter.

title: Amazon Earnings: Return to Profitability But Slow Growth Signaled Ahead
description: The e-commerce giant, which also turned a profit in its latest quarter, indicated sales in the holiday period might rise at their lowest level since 2001.

title: Elon Musk Reaches Out to Advertisers Ahead of Deadline for Twitter Deal
description: The billionaire posted a note to advertisers saying he wanted the service to be “the most respected advertising platform.”

title: Chip Makers, Once in High Demand, Confront Sudden Challenges
description: Demand for semiconductors was off the charts last year. But a sharp slowdown coupled with new U.S. restrictions against China have created obstacles.
